 should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/5712/', '', 'Naltrexone, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', '', 1767369485);
